e 2020 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"a mentor\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"those games\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete-coach duo will join forces once again in Paris.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999908248235269, \"rank\": 9.17526070424341e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete-coach duo\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"forces\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arop will begin the 800-meter on Aug. 7, but Woods will start coaching Canada's track and field team on Aug. 1 as that's when the competition kicks off.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arop_language\", \"score\": 0.9479947370542557, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arop_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arop_language\"}, {\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9978473322721391, \"rank\": 0.0021547886372425976, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 800-meter\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods spoke during a recent press conference about Mississippi State, Team Canada, Arop and more.Here's the full transcript: What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s it like getting to coach a guy that you were able to coach in Mississippi State and now getting to coach him in the Olympics?\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999093256561, \"rank\": 9.067410920504166e-08, \"text\": \"Mississippi State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\"}, {\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9707357044339329, \"rank\": 0.029992171498729715, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999093256561, \"rank\": 9.067410920504166e-08, \"text\": \"Mississippi State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"a recent press conference\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"Arop\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"the full transcript\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"a guy\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a really exciting time, personally, to be able to see the athletes to go through Mississippi State and then also going to perform and compete at the absolute highest level of track and field.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999093256561, \"rank\": 9.067410920504166e-08, \"text\": \"Mississippi State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"the absolute highest level\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So for me, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just a huge blessing.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to take any other credit, because those are the guys that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s out there getting it done on the track.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any other credit\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having run the 800m yourself and having once set the school record, what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s it like to see all the other guys, including Marco, just sort of build on your legacy there and then get to coach him in your event on this big world stage?\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the school record\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"all the other guys\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"your legacy\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"your event\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"this big world stage\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just I just see myself as a stepping stone for those kids to kind of go from high school to college, and then from college to the professional ranks.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stepping stone\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"those kids\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"the professional ranks\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it is a testament to all the hard work that goes into training an athlete and I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t take all the credit for that.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a testament\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"all the hard work\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"all the credit\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have amazing facilities there.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing facilities\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have an amazing training staff, obviously, those guys had amazing training partners in their teammates while they were at Mississippi State, so I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t take all the credit, I would never do that because it really is a team effort.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999093256561, \"rank\": 9.067410920504166e-08, \"text\": \"Mississippi State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing training staff\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"those guys\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"amazing training partners\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"their teammates\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"all the credit\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"a team effort\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just really flattering to see all the hard work, not just from the individuals that made the games but also from the individuals that helped those guys make it to the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"all the hard work\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"the individuals\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the individuals\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"those guys\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you always know that like Marco would potentially be this special at track and field or did you just see see him kind of just grow and develop in his time at Mississippi State and just see it continue to grow once he decided to go professional?\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2382, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999093256561, \"rank\": 9.067410920504166e-08, \"text\": \"Mississippi State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a little bit of both.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marco is one of those guys that when he walks into the room, you kind of know that whatever he does, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s special at it.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"those guys\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It could be playing tic-tac-toe.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tic-tac-toe\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he walks in the room, he just has an aura about him that you know he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to be one of the best guys.\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"an aura\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"the best guys\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s something I picked up on in the recruiting process and then just to see his development over the over the course of time.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the recruiting process\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"his development\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just been really incredible because not everybody comes in with these kinds of dreams and these aspirations, but to see a kid follow through and then accomplish those dreams and aspirations is really, really special and.\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"not everybody\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"these kinds\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"these aspirations\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"those dreams\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"aspirations\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Really they truly are the once in a lifetime type of athletes and Marco is one of them.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lifetime type\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the training process really look like when you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re getting ready for such a big event like the Olympics?\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the training process\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"such a big event\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How do you get them ready, both physically and mentally, to run the race of their life there?\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"their life\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a great question because there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lot that goes into preparing for the Olympic Games, and it goes so far beyond the physical preparation.\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a great question\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3466}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"the physical preparation\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mental preparation is really key, because four years is a long time, right?\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mental preparation\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everybody kind of goes into the Olympic Games with this extra amount of pressure, because there is no next season, when you talk about the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everybody\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"this extra amount\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"no next season\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3784}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s finite, it is it is it is final.\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The hard part about this level is not necessarily developing the talent, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s making sure that as a coach that you are getting into the athletes psyche in a positive way, and you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re able to push them mentally.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 4078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hard part\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3895}, {\"ngram\": \"the talent\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 3936}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes psyche\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4018}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive way\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4036}, {\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you get to this level, everybody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s talented.\", \"from\": 4079, \"to\": 4130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4105}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The separation comes from the mental side of it, and Marco just has nerves of steel.\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The separation\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4145}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental side\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4172}, {\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4189}, {\"ngram\": \"nerves\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4205}, {\"ngram\": \"steel\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I go back to our 2020 Olympic Games over in Tokyo, which due to the pandemic didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t take place until 2021.\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4260, \"end\": 4265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9996057272451832, \"rank\": 0.00039422894496810284, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our 2020 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 4307, \"to\": 4312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marco, unfortunately, did not make the finals of those Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4330}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"those Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a really devastating blow for him as an athlete, that was a really devastating blow for me as a coach and us as a collective.\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really devastating blow\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"a really devastating blow\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4505}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4512}, {\"ngram\": \"a collective\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That hurt us bad.\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, after failing to qualify for the finals, me and Marco, we sat and had lunch together.\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4601}, {\"ngram\": \"Marco\", \"from\": 4610, \"to\": 4615}, {\"ngram\": \"lunch\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We made some promises to each other about our preparation and things that we were both going to change as an athlete and what I was going to change as a coach, and you got to think that was back in July or August of 2021.\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some promises\", \"from\": 4656, \"to\": 4669}, {\"ngram\": \"our preparation\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4716}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4764}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4850}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 4854, \"to\": 4860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, those same things, and those same discussions that we were having in 21, are now starting to come into fruition.\", \"from\": 4870, \"to\": 4987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those same things\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4892}, {\"ngram\": \"those same discussions\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"fruition\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 4986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s so much more than just physical preparation, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s emotional preparation, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mental preparation, and spiritual preparation.\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just physical preparation\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5040}, {\"ngram\": \"emotional preparation\", \"from\": 5051, \"to\": 5072}, {\"ngram\": \"mental preparation\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"spiritual preparation\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those are all things that we have to take into account when we train, not just the physical aspect.\", \"from\": 5130, \"to\": 5229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5150}, {\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\": 5177, \"to\": 5184}, {\"ngram\": \"not just the physical aspect\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"University-wise, what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s it like getting to represent Mississippi State at the world level?\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5286, \"end\": 5303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mississippi_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999093256561, \"rank\": 9.067410920504166e-08, \"text\": \"Mississippi State\", \"types\": [\"Q4322